{
  "stem": "20800.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was on the train too, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We see this, in Buchenwald, when we arrived in Buchenwald, first of all, we saw a lot of German shepherds, a lot of dogs, with those-- German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they was calling SS men, SS, and woman SS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they come to everyone, two, three, or four of them with a dog.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Opened the door, and set, out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Raus, raus, we knew, out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took us all in one-- there was-- I remember we had to go through a big-- not fence, but door-- not door.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arch, gate, a big gate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went through this gate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us all in a room, the women separate, men separate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we women went to one room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] They told us to take off everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a big basin, or what, over the ground, a big one, like this high.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they told us to jump, take off everything, and to jump there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all jumped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was white water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I found it was sort of disinfection to take the things that you might have brought there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from there on, they-- they give us some new dresses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took away all we had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We have to get some new-- new or old, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they give us something to dress in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took us in one block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We all-- all 61 of them in one block were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that was a downstairs in a cellar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a big room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was tables, and there was little rooms where it was the beds for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After all what-- what we went through, we were really happy to be there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
